      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle has plenty of character and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical attention and cosmetic love to get back to its best, it offers a great foundation for someone handy looking for a bargain.",
