    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, a true testament to pride of ownership. Meticulously maintained to the highest standards, this car remains in pristine, showroom condition both aesthetically and mechanically. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a level of care rarely seen in the pre-owned market. This is a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection and unrivaled quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
